name: Mesa Convention Center
notes: This is a first-dose event for MODERNA vaccine, for those 65 years and older. Please note that to successfully book an appointment, each individual must be registered under their own unique email account. The system will not recognize or allow secondary users or dependents to be scheduled under another person's account and will automatically cancel some appointments. To schedule appointments for multiple people, you will need to create an account for each, or contact tech support for help with scheduling. 602-542-1000 (Mon-Fri 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM) Photo ID is required, must include date of birth for 65+ qualification, and bring appointment confirmation email. No walk ins allowed.
